Get a Resource's Entity Set

get_resource_entity_set.Rd

All possible FHIR Resources can be returned as a character vector with list_resources.

get_resource_entity_set(
  resource,
  base_url = "http://hapi.fhir.org/baseR4",
  delay = 5,
  user_agent
)

Arguments

resource

FHIR resource.
base_url

Base url.
delay

Delay in seconds before making the API call.
user_agent

(Optional) User agent.

Value

A fhir_test_api class object.

Examples

library(FHIRworks)
get_resource_entity_set(resource = "Patient")
